          {
            "title": "The Promotion That Came With a Catch",
            "when": "age 30",
            "event": "Priya was promoted to senior analyst at her Pune-based firm, but the role came with no salary hike for 18 months due to a company restructuring freeze, precisely when she and her husband were planning for their child's arrival.",
