            "title": "The Hospital Bill After Aryan's Birth",
            "when": "age 31",
            "event": "After her son Aryan was born with a minor breathing complication requiring a 48-hour NICU stay, the final hospital bill was nearly double what their insurance covered, forcing her to liquidate a short-term mutual fund at a slight loss.",
