          "original": "Better apartment, family trips, maybe a car upgrade",
          "replacement": "Better apartment in a gated community, family trips to Ooty, maybe a car upgrade",
          "attribute_source": "location.city + lifestyle.aspiration"
        },
        {
          "original": "I'll ask two or three people I trust what they paid",
          "replacement": "I'll ask two or three people I trust what they paid \u2014 my colleagues at work, neighbors in Kondapur, maybe someone from my MBA cohort",
          "attribute_source": "location.city + education.postgraduate + behavior.peer_influenced"
        },
        {
